sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (WBJE UI/API)
    participant JC as JobController
    participant JS as JobService
    participant JM as JobDTOMapper
    participant JR as JobRepository
    participant DB as Database

    C->>JC: POST /jobs (JobRequestDTO)
    JC->>JS: createJob(request)

    JS->>JS: validateRequest(request)\n- request != null\n- request.jobDate != null

    JS->>JM: toEntity(request)
    JM->>JM: new JobEntity(request.jobDate)\nsetJobNumber(...)\nsetJobName(...)\nsetCylinderWidth(...)\nsetCylinderCircumference(...)\nsetInfo(...)

    alt noteInfo is aanwezig
        JM->>JM: new NoteEntity(noteInfo)\njob.setNote(note)
    end

    JS->>JR: save(jobEntity)
    JR->>DB: INSERT Job (+ Note indien aanwezig)
    DB-->>JR: persisted JobEntity (met gegenereerde id)

    JS->>JM: toDto(savedEntity)
    JM-->>JS: JobResponseDTO

    JS-->>JC: JobResponseDTO
    JC-->>C: HTTP 201 Created (JobResponseDTO)
